-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>8.</strong></span>鼻梁：塑造更自然高挺的鼻梁</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>9.</strong></span>面颊<span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\"> </span>：改善凹陷的面颊，塑造更年轻的轮廓</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>10.</strong></span>八字纹：用伊婉轻松完成逆生长</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>11.</strong></span>丰唇：塑造充满魅力的嘴唇</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>12.</strong></span>下巴：改善下巴形状，塑造小巧鹅蛋脸</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>13.</strong></span>整个面部：塑造立体五官</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 96, 146);\"><strong>【部位用量参考】</strong></span><strong style=\"font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(2, 53, 185); text-align: center;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060244276930.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"float: left;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 53, 185); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 53, 185); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 53, 185); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 53, 185); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 53, 185); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 53, 185); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 53, 185); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 96, 146); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>【伊婉玻尿酸特点】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060222771315.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"float: left;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>·高浓度</strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><strong>, </strong></span><strong>高分子量</strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><strong>, </strong></span><strong>高品质</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">LG</span>生命科学的非动物源透明质酸原料，使用<span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">15</span>积累本社自主技术<span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">HESH</span>，是韩国使用国内技术开发的首款纯透明质酸填充剂原料。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>·优越的弹性</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">伊婉具有高剪切储能模量。填充剂<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">G</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">”</span>值越高，对经常运动的部位支撑<span style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">(</span>越强、效果越持久）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>·优越的粘性</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">伊婉具有低剪切损失模量。填充剂<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">G</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">”</span>值越低，粘性越强，越不容易离散，更能保持原型。此外，即使频率变化，<span style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">G”</span>仍相对平稳，显示交联稳定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>·终端灭菌系统</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">伊婉经<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">9</span>阶段工艺制造，包括<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">2</span>次灭菌系统工艺，远离污染因子。先做制造准备，溶解透明质酸，再通过特殊技术交联，然后清洗去除可能产生的异物。之后，再粉碎调匀粒子大小，使用<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">100<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">℃</span></span>以上高温无菌工艺将透明质酸原液灭菌。灭菌后，充入针筒，再灭菌包装。包装采用发泡板，彻底阻断流通过程可能发生的污染。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif; white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>·一体型注射器</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-size: 18px;\">	</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">伊婉为保障注射器使用安全，考虑到透明质酸注入便利，在针体设计与流通过程中使用一体设计与发泡包装，阻断污染，荣获<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">2012</span>年第<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">12</span>届韩国商品大奖赛<span style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">“</span>设计<span style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">”</span>奖。针体方便灭菌，使用特殊<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">COC</span>材料，保证原液安全性不受影响。<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">COC</span>材料经物理、化学生物学安全性试验，较之玻璃材料更不易破损，为注射安全提供保障。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 96, 146); font-size: 16px;\"><strong>【真人案例】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060217575592.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">无恢复期，立即见效</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 96, 146); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>【注意事项】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><strong>1.</strong></span>术后要饮食清淡，避免食用刺激性食物和易过敏的食物，忌烟酒；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><strong>2.</strong></span>术后不要在注射部位冰敷或热敷，尽量保持皮肤清洁干燥，避免沾水，注意防晒；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><strong>3.</strong></span>术后后<span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">24</span>小时内尽量避免接触注射部位，避免有大幅度的面部表情动作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><strong>4.</strong></span>术后不要特别在治疗部位按摩，也不要服用活血化瘀的药物。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 3.8px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 96, 146); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>【玻尿酸Q&amp;A】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 3.8px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong>Q:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><strong>如何避免注射假冒玻尿酸？</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong>A:</strong></span>正规机构规定使用合格产品，不要去美容院、小作坊等，另外，产品上贴的标签都有防伪标示，可以查询。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong>Q:</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><strong>注射玻尿酸相对其它塑形手术有什么优势？</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong>A</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong>：</strong></span>因为玻尿酸是人体自身皮肤组织之一，在人体内停留时间短，会在<span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">6-12</span>个月左右被人体分解掉，不会有副作用，过敏反应少；且注射法，局部仅有微胀微痛感，容易接受。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong>Q</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong>：</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><strong>玻尿酸一年进行几次？</stron