in-height: 15px;\"><br/></p>',4,0,100,3800,6800),(90,'201606020001',1,1,3,'【朝阳区 蓝色港湾】激光脱腋毛/唇毛包干，告别来自“猩猩的你”','脱毛 腋毛 唇毛 包干 常好 常好丽格',380000,'/包干','/包干',1.00,38000,10000,-1,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,'独家优惠,聚会美独家,限时优惠',0,0,0,NULL,'2016-06-02 10:44:10','2016-08-08 06:44:19','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>【推荐理由】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">夏天因为腋毛不敢穿无袖装可还行，特价包脱来啦。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【有效期】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">下单后一个月内预约到院。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【流程】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072513498719.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">【项目介绍】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">炎炎夏日，身体的毛毛影响了我们想美的欲望，这些毛毛再也不想要！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">剃毛器——这种暂时性的脱毛方法可以使皮肤在短时间内感觉光洁，但随着时间的推移，新的汗毛会迅速长出来，那么再刮掉或剃掉，反复几次，会使汗毛变得又黑又粗又硬……</span><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">PASS~</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">拔毛——虽然拔毛的过程有些痛苦且耗时，但是与其它脱毛方法相比，这种方式更显经济实惠。汗毛一旦被拔掉，细菌就可能通过原来汗毛的孔进入到毛囊，引起毛囊炎，单个的毛囊炎称着疖，一个以上连起称为痈，都可能引转移性感染。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>PASS~</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 24px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 24px;\">脱毛膏——是一种化学制剂，利用其中的化学物质溶解毛发结构，以达到脱毛的目的。但此方法对毛囊没有任何破坏，故持续时间不长，大概三天左右就会再长出来。脱毛膏化学成分对皮肤有刺激，频繁使用或敏感皮肤会造成毛孔粗大，红肿过敏，甚至发生皮疹，敏感体质的人应该慎用。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 24px;\">PASS~</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 24px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">既然这几种方法都不靠谱，怎么才能摆脱这多余的讨厌的毛毛呢？</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060224029383.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">选择激光脱毛，做“光滑”女神。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>【激光脱毛原理】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">激光脱毛可选择性地穿透到毛囊部位，被毛囊中的黑色素吸收，产生选择性<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">破坏</span>作用，使毛囊变性，萎缩，达到永久性脱毛作用，因而毛发越粗越黑，它的毛囊越大，黑色素越深，更容易接受激光对它的破坏作用故疗效越好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060293484287.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 310px; height: 190px;\" width=\"310\" height=\"190\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">激光脱毛通常一次治疗后能就看到毛发脱落。随着治疗次数的增多，毛发会越来越稀疏、细小，生长速度也会越来越慢。<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(255, 126, 50);\">一般</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 126, 50);\"><strong>3-5</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(255, 126, 50);\">次后</span>就达到永久脱毛的效果。即使多年后又有新的毛囊产生，其毛发也会更加纤细、浅淡，不会造成视觉上的困扰。而且，随着毛囊密度的减少，毛发颜色的减淡，脱毛的疼痛感也会越来越轻。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>【激光脱毛优势】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一、直击毛根，永不再生</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">激光脱毛可穿透表皮，进入真皮内，将毛囊和毛干彻底收缩，产生永久性</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">除毛。而毛囊周边其他嘴直内不含黑素颗粒所以不吸收这种激光，不会产生伤害，更安全更彻底。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">二、世界顶尖的技术，除毛的金标准</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">率先引进全球首创的除毛设备，除毛快速彻底、安全无痛，效果优于一机多用的其它光学设备。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">三、效果立竿见影</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">激光脱毛采用经典半导体除毛激光脱毛技术，它的波长<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">810nm</span>长能穿透至真皮的深层以及皮下脂肪组织。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">四、安全无痛</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">这种除毛的技术降低了单次照射热能量而增加了照射频次。不影响排汗</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">，在治疗时另有稀有翠绿宝石治疗光头，治疗中翠绿宝石窗口紧贴皮肤，使局部表皮冷却至</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">度，有效地保护了正常皮肤不受热损伤，在治疗过程中无任何不适感。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">要阳光，不要阳刚，再见，唇毛</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060243863306.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">没有外漏烦恼，更能随心所欲，再见，腋毛</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060274447169.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【激光脱毛术前术后注意事项】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">术前注意事项：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">1</span>、激光脱毛前要确保皮肤不会受到刺激和伤害。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">2</span>、激光脱毛前两周不要使用脱毛膏、蜜蜡脱毛或其他易造成皮肤敏感的脱毛产品和脱毛方法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">3</span>、激光脱毛前不能暴晒皮肤，因为激光脱毛前暴晒的皮肤很可能已经灼伤皮肤，使皮肤发红、起泡，不利于治疗。另外，脱毛前还要注意自己是否有光过敏史。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">4</span>、激光脱毛前最好将脱毛部位清洗干净。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">5</span>、女性朋友要避开月经期在进行激光脱毛。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">术后注意事项：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">1</span>、脱毛后请避免日晒，并使用医生指示的防晒乳液敷于患部以减少阳光照射。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">2</span>、一周内不能吃辛辣的食物。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Calibri;\">3</span>、</span>激光脱毛后，要注意脱毛部位的清洁卫生，因为游泳馆的水域环境不是很健康，所以在脱毛后的一段时间最好不要去游泳。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【激光脱毛禁忌症】</strong></span></p><ol class=\"custom_num list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"\"><li class=\"list-num-1-1 list-num-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">对光过敏者及进期有应有光敏感药物或激素类药物的就医者。</span></p></li><li class=\"list-num-1-2 list-num-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">妊娠期的女性禁止做此项治疗。</span></p></li><li class=\"list-num-1-3 list-num-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">皮肤近期或者正在进行换肤治疗的就医者。</span></p></li><li class=\"list-num-1-4 list-num-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">皮肤较黑的，有炎症的或不明病因色素点的就医者。</span></p></li><li class=\"list-num-1-5 list-num-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">血液和免疫系统，过敏性皮肤病并及瘢痕体质的就医者。</span></p></li><li class=\"list-num-1-6 list-num-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">近期治疗前2周内暴晒过将受暴晒的不易接受治疗。</span></p></li><li class=\"list-num-1-7 list-num-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">慢性传染病及心脑血管疾病治疗期。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); fo