/2016072513498719.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">【项目介绍】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">瘦腿针<b>，</b>跟瘦脸针一样，只是注射部位和用量有区别，学名A</span><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">型肉毒杆菌毒素，是一种神经传导的阻断剂，用以治疗过度活跃的肌肉。也是一种天然纯化的蛋白质，就是它！拯救你的大粗腿，同时紧致你的腿部肌肤。</span></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060280485349.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 3.8px; margin-bottom: 3.8px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">衡力肉毒素是由我国兰州生物制品研究所研究生产的纯生物制剂，注射后可干扰乙酰胆碱从神经末梢的释放，阻断神经兴奋的传播，使肌纤维不能收缩后，达到安全瘦身的效果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">完美大长腿的理想腿长：身高<span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">X 0.47</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">然而，我们改变不了腿长，</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">BUT</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"></span>，</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">我们可以机智的改变视觉效果</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060277620398.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">=======================</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">瘦腿针（肉毒素）治疗步骤</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-size: 14px;\">1、确定注射位置</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span>双手扶墙踮起脚尖，标记注射点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060258789897.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\">2</span>、冰敷麻醉</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">腿部2-3分钟后会感觉有点冰，但可以忍受。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060241450242.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\">3</span>、表皮消毒</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">用酒精对小腿进行消毒，消毒时不会把标记点擦掉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060244513084.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\">4</span>、注射肉毒素</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">冰敷麻醉后注射时不会很痛，只有微微蚂蚁叮咬的感觉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060253452974.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>【温馨提示】</strong></span>注射瘦腿针前三天可能会感觉小腿酸软有点使不上力，一般一周左右这种感觉就会好转。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 7.5px; margin-bottom: 7.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060276234113.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>【瘦腿针优势】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\">1</span>、持久高效：肉毒素令内外侧肌肉同步放松，腿型瘦得更持久完美。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">2</span>、快速简单：注射方式，午休时间轻松实现瘦小腿。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">3、</span>无疤无痕：注射瘦小腿无需麻醉，只需在两侧小腿肌肉肥厚处选择几个注射点，进行适量的注射即可，只需要十多分钟，无创伤、无疤痕，不影响正常生活。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060252694979.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>【如何维持持久效果】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>连续注射3次</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(50, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">注射完肉毒素两周之后就可以感觉小腿曲线开始变化，这样的变化要到1-2个月达到顶点，保持瘦腿的效果通常为6到8</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">个月。如果想维持更好的瘦腿效果，需要第一次注射瘦腿针后3</span></font><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">个月后再注射第2</span></font><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">针，之后过3</span></font><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">个月再注射第3</span></font><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">针。这样连续注射3</span></font><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">次以上，可以让腿部保持瘦腿效果长达3-5</span></font><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">年之久。</span></font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>做好术后护理</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">如果注射过后细心护理，可以让瘦腿的效果维持更久。反之，如果你没有护理好，也可能导致瘦腿针的效果很快就过去。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">瘦腿针的注意事项【术后护理】</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(187, 46, 83);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica