0);\"><br/></span></strong></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 26px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">润•百颜</span></strong><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">是首个获得中国食品药品监督管理局（CFDA）批准，用于美容整形的国产纯透明质酸填充剂。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-left: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">l 透明质酸是人的皮肤中天然存在的多糖，具有维持皮肤水分、营养皮肤、抗衰老特性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-left: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">l 人体内大量存在的透明质酸与其他物种体内的透明质酸完全相同，没有种属差异，不会引起过敏反应。透明质酸填充剂可以在人体内完全降解，不会造成副作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-left: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;\">l 润•百颜，作为非动物来源修饰透明质酸填充剂，美容整形效果卓然，治疗过程简单安全，快速有效。采用注射方法，达到美容整形的效果，避免手术风险。注射后即可以看到效果，恢复时间短，基本不会影响使用者的日常生活。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060280446869.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 24px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\">★通俗点说<strong>玻尿酸面部填充</strong>就是将玻尿酸以填充物的方式注入於真皮皱褶凹陷或欲丰润的部位。如嘴唇，脸颊，鼻梁，下巴，疤痕等处。可达到立即性的除皱与塑形的效果。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0\"><br/></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">【部位用量参考】</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:white\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(250, 192, 143);\">部位 &nbsp; 注射量</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">鼻子</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 1ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">嘴唇 </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">下巴 </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;1-2ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">苹果肌</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> &nbsp; 2-3ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">太阳穴</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> &nbsp; 2-3ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">额头 </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;2-3ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">法令纹</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;1ml</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">鱼尾纹</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> &nbsp;0.5-1ml</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">【玻尿酸面部填充——打造完美脸型案例】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">01 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">秀气鼻子</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">修饰鼻形，对于手术恐惧或想先适应鼻子垫高样子的人，或只想稍微修饰鼻形，可以考虑玻尿酸注射。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060244217068.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">02 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">饱满太阳穴</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">玻尿酸丰太阳穴，摆脱尖酸刻薄形象，告别&quot;苦瓜脸&quot;。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060255185437.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">03 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">尖俏下巴</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">加长下巴后侧面线条，使其更明显、突出和立体。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060208952568.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">04 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">水润Q唇</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">美化唇型，让双唇丰满水润，性感撩人。</span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060200764496.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\";margin-bottom:0;line-height:28p