e=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 218, 169);\">自体脂肪填充</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 218, 169);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">是从人体自身某些部位吸取多余的皮下脂肪细胞，然后经过吸出的混合物经净化处理、注入药物得到复合脂肪颗粒，选择完整的颗粒脂肪细胞通过注射的方式再移植到自己需要进行脂肪填充的部位，例如乳房、面部等，用以治疗胸部扁平、两侧乳房不对称、浅表微细皱纹、薄嘴唇隆成厚嘴唇、太阳穴、苹果肌填充等等。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-indent: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 26px\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060666551784.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\";text-indent: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 26px\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>【自体脂肪填充适用于什么情况?能够解决哪些问题？】</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-family: 宋体;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">·</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">改变面部轮廓</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">通过自体脂肪可以用来填充额头、眉部、苹果肌、鼻梁和下巴,达到五官、颜面部的更协调。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">·<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">改善皮肤质地</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">面部衰老的原因,除了皮肤松弛出现皱纹外,皮下组织量的减少也是主要原因,自体脂肪的填充可以补充软组织容量不足,使皮肤质地改善,从而达到面部年轻化效果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">·<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">颜面部的不对称畸形</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">主要是先天发育不对称、后天的半侧颜面萎缩、或者是外伤、烧伤后形成的颜面部凹陷；现在比较多的是因为做了双眼皮、眼袋或者是吸脂、溶脂等一些美容手术人为地造成的一些面部凹陷不对称。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060264341567.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">【自体脂肪填充Q&amp;A】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Q:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">自体脂肪填充是永久的吗？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">A:</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">第一次进行自体脂肪填充，脂肪的存活率会达到40%<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">左右，在进行第二次的填充后，一般会达到永久效果。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060210187480.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Q:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">填充后的脂肪会移位?会下垂吗?</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">A:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">面部脂肪填充后,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">如果不受外力或者是表情肌收缩明显</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">脂肪是不会移位和下垂的。所以</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">手术后不能做按摩</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">或是睡觉侧卧压迫填充脂肪的部位。睡觉时需要准备个特别软的枕头</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">如果侧卧了</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">也不会压迫。等手术后</span>2<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">周左右</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">脂肪成活后</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">填充的脂肪就都会长在填充的区域</span>,<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">按压和表情也不会让脂肪移位了。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Q：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">自体脂肪填充有什么优势？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">自体脂肪填充第一特性：不排异，</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">因为完全取自于自身，比较安全，一般不会出现排异反应及副作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">自体脂肪填充第二特性：安全便捷，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">自体脂肪填充本身创口小，出血少，恢复又快。一般手术后2~3<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">天肿胀比较明显</span>,<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">一周左右就能消肿了</span>,<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">一周之后可以正常化妆和出行。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">3.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">自体脂肪填充第三特性：唤醒皮肤活力，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">人体脂肪内含有丰富的活性物质，填充进人体后可以重新激活细胞的活力，促进胶原蛋白再生。常常使皮肤变得又白又嫩。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【自体脂肪填充术后注意事项】</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060296024304.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">术后口服消炎药3天预防感染。<br/></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">吸脂区域必须穿戴紧身衣或者紧包绷带,前一周全天24小时带,特别是前三天,起止血作用；一周后取开,换成一般的紧身衣即可,对身材塑形有用。<br/></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3.</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">面部填充区前三天冰敷,不能按压、按摩,面部填充区域不能做表情、前一周吃流食,减少咀嚼,填充部位表情肌活动影响脂肪成活；术后5-7天拆线。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>做完自体脂肪填充后</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">再来个鼻综合</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">从此屌丝逆袭白富美</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">走上康端大道</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">【关于隆鼻，你可以选择的假体有哪些？】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1、硅胶</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">是目前最常用的隆鼻材料，手术操作起来简便，效果也很理想，价格低廉，具有较好的弹性，手感柔软，易塑形，具有良好的生物相容性，而且也很少出现并发症。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2、膨体</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">从医学角度来说，膨体是最为理想的生物组织代用品，人体组织细胞及血管可长入其特有的微孔结构中，形成组织连接，就和自体组织一样，术后效果更自然，价格比硅胶高。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3、自体软骨</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">具有自体组织无排异的特性，此法隆鼻适用于鼻形的整体塑造以及专门的鼻尖塑形，它与鼻尖处软骨兼容性最好，最逼真。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060239215186.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【隆鼻Q&amp;A】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Q:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">隆鼻后还能愉快的挖鼻孔吗？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">隆鼻后一周不能粗鲁的挖鼻孔喔，也不要触摸、挤压、碰击局部；两周后可以尝试用棉签轻轻地擦出来，不要太过用力，但是一般打喷嚏、擤鼻涕是不会对假体产生任何影响的；等3个月完全回复后，你就可以像以前一样愉快的挖鼻孔啦！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Q:</span></strong><strong>应该选择柳叶型假体还是L型假体？</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">既往若只抬高鼻根部，不考虑抬高鼻尖，一般选用柳叶型，既抬高鼻根部，又抬高鼻尖的，可以选择L型隆鼻假体。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【隆鼻术后注意事项】</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060249658932.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1、假体隆鼻手术后尽可能平躺，垫高头部和背部，有益减少肿痛，局部冰敷能有效减少疼痛，术后5天过后应局部热敷，有助康复；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">2<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\">、假体隆鼻手术后，伤口涂抗生素油膏，如有少量渗血，可用消毒棉纤轻轻搽去，切不可用不清洁的东西接触伤口，以免污染；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">3<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\">、若伤口积存了血痂，可用</span>3%<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\">的双氧水轻轻洗去，再用生理盐水清洗一遍，涂少量药膏，或撒消炎粉让伤口保持干燥，等待自行愈合；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">4<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\">、假体隆鼻术后应尽可能减少活动，尤其是面部活动，平躺静养，避免频繁摘戴眼镜等活动；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">5<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\">、隆鼻术后禁烟禁酒，不要吃辛辣刺激性食物，多吃高蛋白食物和新鲜的蔬菜，一旦出现任何不良反应，及时与医生沟通消除隐患。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【自体脂肪填充+</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">鼻综合 真人案例】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060279486838.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060254712377.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong