left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">埋线提升</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【埋线提升可解决问题】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060303416408.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">紧致提升：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">强力提升下垂面部、颈部肌肤、并可进行胸部提升、臀部提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">抗衰除皱：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">改善法令纹、木偶纹、鱼尾纹、口角纹、额部皱纹等。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">雕塑线条：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">可解决双下巴、婴儿肥、面部肌肤不紧致、面颊凹陷的烦恼。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">改善肤质：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">肤质紧致有弹性、缩小毛孔，亮白润泽。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">“埋线提升”通过埋线的方式来提升肌肤松弛。刺激真皮层的胶原蛋白和细胞组织，令胶原蛋白和细胞组织能围绕所埋入肌肤的细线而增生，达到整体提升的效果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PDO<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">蛋白线</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">是运用获得视频药品管理局（<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">FDA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）最高安全等级认证的可吸收缝线</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">PDO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Fine Thread</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">埋入真皮层里作用，利用异物反应原理，促进皮肤真皮层较远的增生，来提拉皮肤和肌肉，增强皮肤弹性，达到回春效果。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PDO<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">蛋白线最初出自韩国，是利用</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">可被人体吸收溶解</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的螺旋栓线插入表层肌肤，从而刺激皮肤下胶原蛋白的再生。<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">PDO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">线最初是用于心脏手术的心脏缝合线，蛋白线植入体内被身体缓缓溶解吸收，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6—8<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个月期间持续的刺激皮肤和筋膜层，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使已经僵硬或下垂的皮下组织重新进行排列，皮肤内的老化胶原被激活，产生新胶原，</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">持续时间一般在<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2—3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">针对以上可改善情况，一般建议：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中面部会用到40<span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到</span>60<span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根，</span>V<span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">脸提升</span>20<span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根左右，全面部</span>60<span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到</span>100<span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据不同用户皮肤松弛程度不一样无法给出具体根数，以上数据均供参考）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">塔阵童颜线</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">，少数同时拥有美国<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">FDA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">及欧盟</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">CE</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">权威认证，是双方向的空心塔体的线体，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">均由可生物吸收的材质制成。</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">通过注射的方式，植入创新设计<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">360°</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">聚乳酸圆锥体（</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">CONE</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）系结状的塑形线，对脸部有明显的提升效果并可很好改善法令纹，拥有</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">V-LINE</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的效果。更能在短时间内刺激皮肤胶原蛋白的再生，增加皮肤的弹性并改善活化肌肤。</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">非手术局麻，治疗时间为<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">30-50</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分钟，术后效果立显，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不影响正常工作生活，完全恢复期为<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天（包含，轻微青紫，针孔恢复），</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">保持效果<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2-3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">革新传统埋线提升只单纯拉紧皮肤表面弊端，采用独特创新<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">360°</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">聚乳酸圆锥体塑形线，</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由国内</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">唯一授权</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">医师叶文珏院长亲自操作，</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">全方位实现<span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">祛除皱纹、提拉松弛下垂组织、美白亮肤</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”3D</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">钻石脸效果，同时能源源不断地促进胶原及弹力蛋白新生。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">针对以上可改善情况，一般建议：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中下面部一般用到2<span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根线</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:30px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据皮肤松弛程度不一样无法给出具体根数，数据供参考）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:48px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:48px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【什么原因会导致面部下垂】</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060325076802.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">·皮下脂肪减少：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">人到了一定年龄后，面部皮肤脂肪会逐渐减少。这种脂肪减少的后果就是面部失去丰满圆润的年轻特征，而显得衰老。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">·面部肌肉的变化及其对表面皮肤的影响：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">面部相关肌肉会因为做表情的需要而不断运动。这种运动会造成皮肤的反复折叠，天长日久，就会在相关部位形成皱纹。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">·组织弹性降低：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">随着年龄的增长，面部软组织的弹性会逐渐降低。弹性降低的结果会使面部软组织受重力的影响而出现松垂。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">·面部骨组织的变化：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">随着年龄逐渐增长，面部相关骨组织会逐渐的被吸收，由此导致面部体积减小。这种体积减小会使人看上去衰老。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【“埋线提升”与“超声刀”&amp;“传统拉皮提升”区别】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">和超声刀区别</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060363332054.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">简单说就是：哪里下垂拉哪里，它起到的是定向提拉作用，比超声刀更有针对性。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">和传统拉皮区别</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">埋线是微创，传统拉皮是手术方式，拉皮会损失20%到30%的表情。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); letter-spacing: 0px;\">传统的拉皮</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">方式是讲求定点和方向来拉扯松弛的皮肤从而达到提升与皮肤紧致的效果，施术部位被限制，而</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); letter-spacing: 0px;\">埋线提升</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">可在任何部位，进行任何方向与角度的提拉，亦可带来长效型紧致拉皮效果，被埋入的特殊医用线是会自然被人体吸收，几乎无任何副作用。恢复期短，可立即见效。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【埋线前后对比图】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060327929913.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【术后注意事项】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">1、避开烟酒、桑拿等外部刺激，不要用力清洗或按压面部。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">2、面部可能出现瘙痒感，切勿经常触摸面部以免诱发炎症。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:26px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">3、一个月内避免做夸张的表情，尽少大幅度牵动面部肌肉