style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">深蓝射频</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></strong></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060677919509.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">深蓝射频主要通过在皮下特定深度内产生40.68MHz的射频场，使皮肤及皮下组织中的极性水分子产生高速旋转震动，从而使组织快速加热。温度的升高促进皮下脂肪的分解代谢，刺激胶原蛋白及弹性纤维的增生重组，达到收紧皮肤，形体的作用。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">脂肪消融：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">微波热塑的热作用深度可达皮下脂肪层，温度的提升可引起促进脂肪代谢的一系列生化反应。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">1、Q10效应 温度每升高10度 体内酶活性就增加一倍。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">2、局部血流加快将脂肪细胞的代谢产物带走。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">3、血液中的氧含量增加。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">4、淋巴引流增强，增加局部贮集体液和代谢产物的排出体外。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">胶原重建：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">热效应刺激胶原母细胞的增生，胶原纤维的重新排列，修复老化受损的胶原层。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">伊肤泉去颈纹微针</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">伊肤泉微针美塑，又称微针中胚层疗法。能瞬间打开通往肌肤基底层的通道，将生长因子源源不断的输送到皮肤底层。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060638648602.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"></span></p><p><br/></p><table width=\"-174\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\" height=\"0\"><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\">疼痛度</strong><br/></p></td><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\" height=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">两颗星</span></td><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\" height=\"0\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>恢复期</strong></span></td><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\" height=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">2—3天</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>治疗时长</strong></span></td><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">120—150分钟</span></td><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\"><strong>麻醉方式</strong></span></td><td style=\"word-break: break-all;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"153\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">表皮麻醉</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px; line-height: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">DNA祛</span></strong><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px; line-height: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">颈纹微针</span></strong><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px; line-height: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">套组</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">针对颈纹所含生物去皱活肤成分，直接作用于断裂的纤维细胞，促进胶原蛋白合成，重新生成纤维组织，舒展干纹和皱纹，逆转衰老状态，重现饱满紧致的肌肤；DNA去皱强化套组——激活自身细胞再生，加强自身合成与分泌机能，内源性补充胶原蛋白和弹力纤维，MT等因子能高效地清除体内自由基，减少生物的氧化和衰老。去皱同时皮肤变得细嫩光滑和紧致亮丽，强烈促进皮肤细胞的分裂和生长。刺激透明质酸，胶原蛋白和糖蛋白等的合成和分泌。使皮肤皱纹自然消失，皮肤恢复光泽和弹性，适合局部皱纹深者。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: normal; line-height: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">【Q&amp;A】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q：市面上一般的去颈纹都是用的玻尿酸填充，这个和玻尿酸有什么区别？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A：玻尿酸一般只能维持半年到一年，但是这个套餐至少可以维持2-3年，综合来说效果和性价比更高。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q：为什么福袋是六次射频和三次微针？这个疗程和单纯的微针去颈纹有什么区别？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A：福袋的项目次数是经过聚会美多方综合调查过的最有效和最高性价比的组合。在微针之前会先用深蓝射频去除掉多余的颈部脂肪，并且刺激皮下胶原增生，修复颈部弹力组织，再配合微针抚平凹陷型断层皱纹，实现一加一大于三的效果。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Q：微针会有什么副作用吗？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A: 与人体100%同源，无任何排异及副作用，安全可靠;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 28px;\">【相关案例】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060650344026.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060692536392.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 宋体, tahoma, Srial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(54, 96, 146); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); line-height: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【医院介绍】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, 宋体, tahoma, Srial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); line-height: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060658824714.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51)