 rgb(0, 176, 240); letter-spacing: 0px;\">护肤防晒</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">→</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); letter-spacing: 0px;\">美美滴离院</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">→</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); letter-spacing: 0px;\">订金退还</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: center;\">【项目介绍】</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">光子嫩肤到底是个啥？</span>】<br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">光子嫩肤<span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;\">利用光子嫩肤仪强脉冲光子产生的光化学作用,刺激肌肤,使真皮层胶原纤维和弹力纤维产生分子结构的化学变化,数量增加,重新排列,恢复其原有的弹性,从而达到消除皱纹和缩小毛孔的治疗效果.另外,它所产生的光热作用可增强血管功能,改善肌肤的微循环。</span><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">光子嫩肤技术是一种非剥脱的物理疗法,具有高度的方向性,很高的密度和连贯性,光子嫩肤可被聚集到很小的治疗部位,因而其作用部位准确,不会对周围组织和皮肤附属器官造成损伤.同时,光子嫩肤非介入的治疗方法适应不同的皮肤状态,安全有效,不会对皮肤造成损坏。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">光子嫩肤可以改善肌肤问题？</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">】</span></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 18px;\">光子嫩肤可以改善皮肤粗糙、红血丝、皮肤暗黄、色沉雀斑、毛孔粗大、痘印痘疤，同时还可以用来除皱。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060689504179.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><br/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">【</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">光子嫩肤治疗后会不会有依赖性，不做会不会老化加快？</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">】</span></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060609542679.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">这是一个大家都关心的问题。我们可以注意到，白种人的皱纹比我们要明显一些，可能就是他们的皮肤对光的抵抗力要差一些的原因。经过光子治疗后，皮肤的结构发生了变化，表现为皮肤中胶元，尤其是弹力纤维的恢复。只要在以后的日子里加强保护<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">，皮肤是不会变本加厉的加速老化的。反而因为它会刺激真皮层的胶原增生，有抗衰的作用，</span>实际上来看，美国是光子嫩肤的发源地，最早接受治疗的也是美国人，有两项非常有影响的研究表明，10年前最早接受光子治疗的人，至今疗效仍然非常满意，并没有出现加速老化的现象。所以治疗后变年轻皮肤是不会加速老化的。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">【</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">哪些人适合做光子嫩肤？</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">】</span></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>1.<span style=\"line-height: 24px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 24px;\">面部皮肤粗糙，毛孔粗大，痘印及面部毛细血管扩张。</span></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>2.</strong>面部开始出现松弛，有细小皱纹，出现老年性皮肤改变。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>3.</strong>皮肤暗黄，想改变皮肤质地，希望皮肤弹性更好的人群。</span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>4.<span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">面部有点状色素斑，无论日光性的还是雀斑，都可以用嫩肤环节的祛斑模式治疗。</span></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><br/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">【</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">光子嫩肤不适宜人群？</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); font-weight: bold;\">】</span></span></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><br style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important\"/></p><p style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap\"><span style=\"font-siz