0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">【项目介绍】</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016061613030405.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 417px; height: 165px;\" width=\"417\" height=\"165\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">瑞蓝(Restylane) 玻尿酸产品由瑞典Q-Med AB生产，是一种知名的、健康且自然的美容填充剂产品。玻尿酸又名透明质酸及糖醛酸，是人体真皮组织的重要成分之一。它是一种无毒性、无排斥、无过敏发炎的皮肤填充产品，与人体兼容性极好，注射后稳定、自然，不移走，又可被吸收，已于2008年12月获得获食品药品检验局批准登录中国。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016061652240907.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 237px;\" width=\"387\" height=\"237\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016061652772501.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 398px; height: 318px;\" width=\"398\" height=\"318\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">★通俗点说<strong>玻尿酸面部填充</strong>就是将玻尿酸以填充物的方式注入於真皮皱褶凹陷或欲丰润的部位。如嘴唇，脸颊，鼻梁，下巴，疤痕等处。可达到立即性的除皱与塑形的效果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background: white;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【部位用量参考】</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 192, 143);\">部位 &nbsp; 注射量</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">鼻子</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 1ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">嘴唇&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; 1ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">下巴&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;1-2ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">苹果肌</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; 2-3ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">太阳穴</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; 2-3ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">额头&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;2-3ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">法令纹</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">鱼尾纹</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;0.5-1ml</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 28px;\">【玻尿酸面部填充——打造完美脸型案例】</strong></span><strong style=\"line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 28px;\"></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">01&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">秀气鼻子</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">修饰鼻形，对于手术恐惧或想先适应鼻子垫高样子的人，或只想稍微修饰鼻形，可以考虑玻尿酸注射。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060244217068.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">02&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">饱满太阳穴</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">玻尿酸丰太阳穴，摆脱尖酸刻薄形象，告别&quot;苦瓜脸&quot;。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060255185437.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"