gin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">汽泡嫩肤:</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">继光子嫩肤后,皮肤治疗领域的全新嫩肤手段。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">生产原理:</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">真空负压技术与超细小微汽泡水的完美结合。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">治疗原理:</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">打通皮肤供氧通道,提高供氧量,加快皮肤整体微循环。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; whi