: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">3、血液中的氧含量增加。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">4、淋巴引流增强，增加局部贮集体液和代谢产物的排出体外。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: normal; line-height: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">胶原重建：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">热效应刺激胶原母细胞的增生，胶原纤维的重新排列，修复老化受损的胶原层。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: normal; line-height: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: normal; line-height: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">伊肤泉去颈纹微针</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: normal; line-height: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\