-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">陈利利医生：</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">我们所采用的是PPDO高分子合成线，是医疗美容领域最新一代的可吸收线。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">小编：</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">PPDO线跟市面上的蛋白线有什么不同?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">陈利利医生：</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">这样讲吧，常见的蛋白线在植入人体后，大多存在自体排异现象，比如容易对黄豆、牛奶啊之类过敏的人。区别于传统的蛋白线、材质不好的化学合成线，我们采用的最先进的可吸收高分子聚合材料——PPDO线，其周身有三维立体分布着锚点(倒刺)，通过线的牵引力可以把鼻子的角度、鼻梁、鼻尖按预期效果来改变。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">小编：</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">埋线隆鼻后是否会青肿?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">陈利利医生：</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">通常这种情况下，需要看表浅层皮肤的毛细血管是否受到了损伤。即使出现，也没有关系的，一般术后3—5天内会自行消退。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">小编：</span>埋的线会不会露出来?</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">陈利利医生：</span>相信这是大家最关注的问题了。正常情况下是不会的，而且我们选择的PPDO线也不存在排期的现象。手术完成后，我们通常都建议受术者术后3天内再来医院复查下，以保障术后的效果及顾客的满意度。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">小编：</span>埋线隆鼻的效果能维持多久呢?</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">陈利利医生：</span>埋线隆鼻最长可维持2年时间哦!奥德丽格采用的最新PPDO线，与别家不同，它可持续刺激你的皮下组织，促进胶原及弹性蛋白的合成。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">小编：</span>最后，能不能请陈医生透露一下你与其他医生的不同之处呢?</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">陈利利医生：</span>这位小编问的好犀利哦，不过也很专业的样子呢。要说我与其他整形医生有什么不一样，可能就是因为我是学精细解剖出身的吧，对面部结构有一定的了解，在埋线过程中可以避免对神经、血管的损伤，所以安全性更高一些，术后效果也更好一些吧。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px;\">【埋线隆鼻前后】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016070762165887.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【术后注意事项】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">1、避开烟酒、桑拿等外部刺激，不要用力清洗或按压面部。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">2、面部可能出现瘙痒感，切勿经常触摸面部以免诱发炎症。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">3、一个月内避免做夸张的表情，尽少大幅度牵动面部肌肉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;\">4、注意均衡饮食、充分休息，避免侧睡对面部造成压迫</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 18px;\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">【相关医院】</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016070114626902.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">奥德丽格——年轻化整形美容基地</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">北京奥德丽格医疗美容是bcc联合丽格医疗美容集团连锁成员。奥德丽格依托“丽格医生”为主体的全球优势医疗资源，以亚洲最高水平的年轻化整形外科医生为主要医疗团队，致力于面部年轻化、自体脂肪移植、胸部整形、注射物取出等方面的学术研究及临床实践，并以科学年轻化、个性年轻化、综合年轻化为美学设计标准，真正将高端医疗美容服务与亚洲权威整形技术相结合，为广大求美者提供科学、安全、诚实、恰当的医疗美容服务。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">未来，丽格医美继续秉承“把美容，托付放心医生”的企业文化理念，全体医护人员誓将坚守“希波克拉底誓言”，用专业医疗技术造就全人类的美丽事业。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px;\">【相关医生】</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016070190335806.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">陈利利医生</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※毕业于大连医科大学整形美容外科</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※师从 中国著名整形外科专家王志军教授&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※主修面部精细解刨学 ，擅长面部埋线提升和注射微整形</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※瑞兰玻尿酸认证注射医师&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※韩国艾丽微全国首批认证注册医师</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※专家技术：精细解剖，对面部组织结构把握精准，对神经，血管损伤最小化</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">※经典术士：面部埋线提升术，全面部注射微雕</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p>',2,8000,100,8000,20600),(140,'201607120001',1,1,1,'【朝阳区 亮马桥】埋线提升？埋线去法令纹？都在这里！','埋线 提升 隆鼻 颈纹 法令纹 奥德丽格',560000,'起','起',7.10,400000,10000,-1,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,'院长亲执,定制咨询,聚会美独家,限时优惠',2,440000,0,NULL,'2016-07-12 19:04:35','2016-07-26 03:46:45','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>【推荐理由】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">独创多层次埋线，大线小线的完美结合，提升逆龄看这里！</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【有效期】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">下单后一个月内预约到院。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【流程】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072501817118.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【价格说明】</strong></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072057097216.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">【项目介绍】</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072015104413.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072021207158.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072063615893.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">PPDO面部埋线提升</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">一次实现&quot;紧肤、提拉、塑形&quot;三大功效</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【埋线提升可解决问题】</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">紧致提升</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：强力提升下垂面部、颈部肌肤、并可进行胸部提升、臀部提升。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">抗衰除皱</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：改善法令纹、木偶纹、鱼尾纹、口角纹、额部皱纹等。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">雕塑线条</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：可解决双下巴、婴儿肥、面部肌肤不紧致、面颊凹陷的烦恼。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">改善肤质</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">：肤质紧致有弹性、缩小毛孔，亮白润泽。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">PPDO线</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">介绍(聚对二氧环己酮)，<strong>PPDO</strong> 是目前市场上唯一通过中国食品药品监督管理局CFDA认证的医用可吸收缝合线，为临床使用多年的外科可吸收生长线，可在人体内安全分解，能被人体完全吸收代谢，有更高的抗张强度，持结性能更好，临床使用更加安全可靠</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072083445551.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">奥德丽格</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">埋线项目独有三大优势：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072024448682.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072075379781.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 40px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072087115555.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【“埋线提升”与“超声刀”&amp;“传统拉皮提升”区别】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">和超声刀的区别</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060363332054.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">简单说就是：哪里下垂拉哪里，它起到的是定向提拉作用，针对性。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">和传统拉皮区别</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">埋线是微创，传统拉皮是手术方式，拉皮会损失<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">20%</span>到<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">30%</span>的表情。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">传统的拉皮方式是讲求定点和方向来拉扯松弛的皮肤从而达到提升与皮肤紧致的效果，施术部位被限制，而埋线提升可在任何部位，进行任何方向与角度的提拉，亦可带来长效型紧致拉皮效果。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">【相关案例】</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072024123998.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\">【术后注意事项】</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span></strong><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">1、避开烟酒、桑拿等外部刺激，不要用力清洗或按压面部。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">2、面部可能出现瘙痒感，切勿经常触摸面部以免诱发炎症。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">3、一个月内避免做夸张的表情，尽少大幅度牵动面部肌肉。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">4、注意均衡饮食、充分休息，避免侧睡对面部造成压迫。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">【相关医院】</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016070114626902.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>奥德丽格——年轻化整形美容基地</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京奥德丽格医疗美容是bcc联合丽格医疗美容集团连锁成员。奥德丽格依托“丽格医生”为主体的全球优势医疗资源，以亚洲最高水平的年轻化整形外科医生为主要医疗团队，致力于面部年轻化、自体脂肪移植、胸部整形、注射物取出等方面的学术研究及临床实践，并以科学年轻化、个性年轻化、综合年轻化为美学设计标准，真正将高端医疗美容服务与亚洲权威整形技术相结合，为广大求美者提供科学、安全、诚实、恰当的医疗美容服务。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">未来，丽格医美继续秉承“把美容，托付放心医生”的企业文化理念，全体医护人员誓将坚守“希波克拉底誓言”，用专业医疗技术造就全人类的美丽事业。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">【相关医生】</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016070190335806.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">陈利利医生</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">※毕业于大连医科大学整形美容外科</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">※师从 中国著名整形外科专家王志军教授&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">※主修面部精细解刨学 ，擅长面部埋线提升和注射微整形</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">※瑞兰玻尿酸认证注射医师&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">※韩国艾丽微全国首批认证注册医师</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">※专家技术：精细解剖，对面部组织结构把握精准，对神经，血管损伤最小化</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">※经典术士：面部埋线提升术，全面部注射微雕</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px;\"><br/></p>',2,4400,100,4000,5600),(141,'201607130001',1,1,1,'【朝阳区 百子湾】超微小气泡+无针水光 拼团 清洁补水 一步到位','超微小气泡 微小气泡 无针水光 清洁 补水 黑头 去黑头 祛黑头 博士园',180000,'/次','/次',3.80,67900,10000,-1,7,0,1,NULL,NULL,'定制咨询,限时优惠,聚会美独家',3,69900,2,NULL,'2016-07-13 14:36:02','2016-08-09 04:58:25','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>【推荐理由】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">夏天清洁不到位，其他护肤全白搭！超微小气泡清洁更彻底，无针水光更让洁净的肌肤不干燥。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【有效期】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">7月31日前到院。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【流程】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072501817118.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【价格说明】</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">原价：1800元/次</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">单独预订：699元/次</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><strong>3人拼团：679/次</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 28px;\">【包含项目】</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">韩国超微小气泡+玻尿酸导入+优斐斯医用面膜</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【项目介绍】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">什么是超微小气泡？</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">汽泡嫩肤：继光子嫩肤后,皮肤治疗领域的全新嫩肤手段。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">生产原理：真空负压技术与超细小微汽泡水的完美结合。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">治疗原理：打通皮肤供氧通道,提高供氧量,加快皮肤整体微循环。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">超微小气泡洗净能力图示：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072065256527.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>项目优势：&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.清洁各种肌肤垃圾，耀出肌肤健康色泽——将超细微小气泡和营养液充分结合，通过特殊设计的螺旋形吸头直接作用于皮肤，且能够保持超细微小气泡长时间接触皮肤，促进剥离作用。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2.祛除角质&amp;皮脂——超微小气泡与吸附作用相结合，在安全没有疼痛的状态下，能深层洁面、祛除老化角质细胞、祛除皮脂、彻底清除毛囊漏斗部的各种杂质、螨虫及油脂残留物。&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3.促进微循环，活肤焕颜——能增加肌肤毛细血管的含氧量，并促进肌肤的血液循环，同时微小气泡中释放的活性氧能给予肌肤抗自由基功效，这些都能抑制肌肤的老化。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">有效的营养能直接给予到肌肤基底层，让肌肤莹润如本初，每一滴水分守护，每一寸水盈弹润，每一天都能感受到肌肤的充盈水分，充沛弹力。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016070154295818.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>适应症：</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">痤疮，闭口，毛囊炎，清螨；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">去黑头，改善皮肤松弛，收细毛孔，增加皮肤透明度；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">皮肤美白，改善皮肤晦暗，暗黄，改善肤质；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">深层清洁皮肤，同时给皮肤补水；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">用于剥脱性皮肤重建术和非剥脱性皮肤重建术的术前术后护理。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 18pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">【注意事项】</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.治疗当天，要仔细清洁面部，不能有化妆品残留。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2.所有保养都是“过犹不及”哦，所以无需频繁进行。就像我们敷面膜一样，大概每周一次就足够了。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3.做完后，多补水保湿，防晒也不能掉以轻心哦~补水补水补水防晒防晒防晒！重要的事情说三遍！</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 18pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">【博士园医疗美容医院】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; list-style-typ