ight: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【流程】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016072501817118.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【价格说明】</strong></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016071502675820.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">【项目说明】</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第一种：茶色黑眼圈（色素型黑眼圈）</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">形成原因：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">生成黑色素体质或代谢不全，日晒等因素造成色素沉淀在眼周，久而久之形成黑眼圈。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">常见人群：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">多年龄层</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">色素型可能更符合人们心目中“黑眼圈”的形象：颜色是褐色或灰色斑点，伴随着皮肤褶皱明显等特征。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">如果用手撑开眼睑皮肤，色素型黑眼圈不会发生任何颜色上的变化。既能在下眼睑出现也可分布于上眼睑</span>，</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">上下眼睑就是我们化妆时候的部位。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016071504567066.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">快速有效方法：</span></strong></span><strong style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">调Q激光+e乐姿ST</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; font-family: &#39;arial black&#39;, &#39;avant garde&#39;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">调Q激光：</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">采用光电原理，让激光透过皮肤表层到达皮肤深层，让皮肤内部的色素颗粒瞬间粉碎，粉碎的<span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">色素颗粒会被人体的巨噬细胞吞噬后，慢慢运走。有效击碎沉着色素，进而改善黑眼圈。</span></span></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016071554490957.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px;\">调Q激光</span>再配合能促使真皮层分泌胶原蛋白的</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">e乐姿ST射频</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">能量，加速眼部新陈代谢，淡化黑眼圈，同时达到眼部皮肤提升紧致。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">第2种：血管型黑眼圈（青色黑眼圈）</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">形成原因：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">局部血液循环不畅</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">常见人群：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">作息不规律的青年人</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">众所周知，眼睑（俗称“眼皮”）是人皮肤最薄的地方之一，甚至薄得透明。加之此处皮肤下脂肪层也很薄甚至没有，因此皮下与肌肉中血管便透出颜色来从而形成黑眼圈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">年龄增大带来的自然老化必然伴随着皮下脂肪的进一步减少与真皮变薄，因此黑眼圈会愈来愈严重。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">用手撑开黑眼圈，皮肤延展得更薄，这里颜色会更明显，这也是血管型的特征之一。（有黑眼圈的童鞋对着镜子试试）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">这就是为什么美白眼霜往往无法解决黑眼圈，美白眼霜只能改善色素问题，对血管无效。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016071592092322.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:17px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">快速有效方法：调Q激光+水光针</span></strong></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">调Q激光：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">采用光电原理，让激光透过皮肤表层到达皮肤深层，让皮肤内部的色素颗粒瞬间粉碎，粉碎的<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">色素颗粒会被人体的巨噬细胞吞噬后，慢慢运走。有效击碎沉着色素，进而改善黑眼圈。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016071554490957.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">再配合<strong>复方水光针