 style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">l 透明质酸是人的皮肤中天然存在的多糖，具有维持皮肤水分、营养皮肤、抗衰老特性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">l 人体内大量存在的透明质酸与其他物种体内的透明质酸完全相同，没有种属差异，不会引起过敏反应。透明质酸填充剂可以在人体内完全降解，不会造成副作用。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060280446869.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">★通俗点说<strong>玻尿酸面部填充</strong>就是将玻尿酸以填充物的方式注入於真皮皱褶凹陷或欲丰润的部位。如嘴唇，脸颊，鼻梁，下巴，疤痕等处。可达到立即性的除皱与塑形的效果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【部位用量参考】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 192, 143);\">部位 &nbsp; 注射量</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">鼻子</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 1ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">嘴唇&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">下巴&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;1-2ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">苹果肌</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2-3ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">太阳穴</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2-3ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">额头&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;2-3ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">法令纹</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);\">鱼尾纹</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;0.5-1ml</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【玻尿酸面部填充——打造完美脸型案例】</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">01&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">秀气鼻子</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">修饰鼻形，对于手术恐惧或想先适应鼻子垫高样子的人，或只想稍微修饰山根，可以考虑玻尿酸注射。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060244217068.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">02&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">饱满太阳穴</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">玻尿酸丰太阳穴，摆脱尖酸刻薄形象，告别&quot;苦瓜脸&quot;。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060255185437.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">03&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">尖俏下巴</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">加长下巴后侧面线条，使其更明显、突出和立体。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060208952568.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">04&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">水润Q唇</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">美化唇型，让双唇丰满水润，性感撩人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060200764496.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">05&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">鼻唇沟注射</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">变浅变舒缓后的鼻唇沟，找回年轻时自然和谐的感觉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060218073468.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">【玻尿酸塑形五大优势】</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">无副作用：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">玻尿酸来自于生物组织，人体皮肤组织不会产生排斥，几乎无任何副作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">安全无痛感：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">采用注射法，像打针一样，局部仅有微胀微痛感，无大痛苦。</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 