176, 80);\">BOTOX瘦脸</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060219829193.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">BOTOX瘦脸针首要作用于肌肉组织，解决咬肌肥大，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">也就是在肌肉肥大处注射肉毒素，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">使该处肌肉松弛、萎缩，咬肌活动减少、萎缩变小。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">BOTOX瘦脸效果</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060244845580.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">注射瘦脸一般在一周到一个月后会有效果，正常情况下，注射BOTOX一周就可以看到效果。两三个月后瘦脸的效果达到顶峰，可将咬肌缩小约30%，因人而异，效果最久可持续约半年到一年。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">平均半年到一年可注射一次，如果在多次注射瘦脸针后，咬肌持续性维持麻痹状态，即可使咬肌永久萎缩、变小，治疗更稳定、更彻底，可达到永久瘦脸的目的。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">（tips：注射瘦脸针对医生的要求非常严格，需要专业措施和丰富经验的医生哦。）</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">适合注射BOTOX瘦脸针的脸型</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060293795300.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">瘦脸针一般是根据脸型选择瘦脸方法，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">但并不是所有脸型都可以通过注射肉毒素来变瘦，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">对于那些皮下脂肪较多的胖脸，还需要针对脸部抽脂或去除颊脂垫来解决。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">而方脸因为下颌角骨头大的，需要做磨骨手术才可以，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">一般情况下，瘦脸针最适合国字脸和咬肌肥大者。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">术后护理</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">·一周之内不能吃抗生素&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">·6小时之内最好保持头部直立，避免扩散</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">·注射6小时内不能洗脸化妆，不能触碰注射部位</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">·一周内禁食辛辣海鲜，禁烟酒</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">·术后一个月内禁止热敷、按摩</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">【相关医院】</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060207077871.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">常好丽格集注射美容、皮肤美容、脂肪移植、面部微雕、产后修复、整形外科、抗衰老等整形美容项目于一体。建立开设“联合丽格脂肪移植中心”，致力于发展自体脂肪移植整形项目的研究，是国内专注于自体脂肪移植的特色整形美容机构。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size: 10.5px; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(2, 53, 185);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>【医生介绍】</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 96, 146);\"></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.aimeipin.cc/textImage/2016060244063831.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC Semibold&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>郭昌灏</strong><strong> &nbsp;</strong><strong>北京常好丽格医疗美容机构院长</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">从事医疗美容行业将近20年，中国整形美容外科知名专家。毕业于北京首都医科大学，师从中国整形外科之父宋儒耀，曾担任国内二级甲等医院、北京史三八整形美容医院、北京京韩整形美容医院特聘专家与院长。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;; min-height: 15px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">全球高端医疗美容连锁品牌联合丽格首批投资医生之一</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">北京常好丽格医疗美容机构院长</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">中国医师协会整形与美容协会会员</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">国际医疗整形美容协会会员<span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">中国中西医协会美容分会专家组成员</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">中国康复医学会美容外科分会委员</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">大韩整形美容外科协会会员<span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">韩国医学科学产业协会会员</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">中日韩整形整形专家交流峰会特约嘉宾</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8px; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">韩国大永整形外科安栋显教授处进修专家</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font